This isn’t what this section is for. I recommend you create a Thread in the “Development Teams” section of the Forums. You’ll also want to include an Application for potential Designers/Developers to fill out. I’ll include an example below. Also, just having a Virtual Private Server won’t be enough to attract serious people. You’ll want to do more than this.

Example of a decent Application:

Development Experiences:

Public Releases and Information:

Do you have experience in Website Design and Development:

Please list any and all Languages which you are knowledgeable of:

Do you have a Certified Diploma or Degree in regards as to Programming:
